label: (Pair of) Jacks or Better
description: Your hand contains two cards with the same value that are Jacks, Queens, Kings, or Aces.

label: Two Pair
description: Your hand has two sets of pairs of any value for each set of pairs. The values of the two pairs are different.

label: Three Of A Kind
description: Your hand has three of the same value card.

label: Straight
description: Your hand has five cards whose values can be arranged in sequence. (e.g. 2-3-4-5-6) An Ace can be a low(lower than 2) or high value(greater than King).

label: Flush
description: Your hand has five cards with the same suit.

label: Full House
description: Your hand has a three of a kind and a pair.

label: Four Of A Kind
description: Your hand has four of the same value card.

label: Straight Flush
description: Your hand fits the definition of a straight and all 5 cards are the same suit.

label: Royal Flush
description: Your hand fits the definition of a straight flush and the sequence of cards is 10-J-Q-K-A.
